---
// Who We Are - Visual Timeline Layout
---

<section class="relative py-20 bg-gradient-to-br from-slate-700 via-blue-700 to-teal-700 overflow-hidden">
  <!-- Subtle Background Pattern -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-5">
    <div class="absolute inset-0" style="background-image: radial-gradient(circle at 25% 25%, white 1px, transparent 1px), radial-gradient(circle at 75% 75%, white 1px, transparent 1px); background-size: 50px 50px;"></div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="relative z-10 max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6">
    <!-- Header -->
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-light text-white mb-8 tracking-wide">
        Who <span class="text-cyan-300 font-normal">We Are</span>
      </h1>
      <div class="w-32 h-px bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-blue-400 to-transparent mx-auto"></div>
    </div>
     
    <!-- Opening Statement -->
    <div class="group transform transition-all duration-500 hover:scale-105 mb-12">
      <div class="bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-xl border border-white/20 rounded-3xl p-8 hover:bg-white/15 hover:border-white/30 transition-all duration-500">
        <p class="text-xl text-blue-100 italic font-light leading-relaxed text-center">
          Water is becoming the world's most critical resource. As scarcity and contamination rise, so does the 
          urgency for bold, scalable solutions.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Blue Economy & Finance Forum Photo -->
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        <img 
          src="/headshots/blue-economy-forum-monaco-2025.jpg" 
          alt="Christoph Schwager and Verena Sturm at the Blue Economy & Finance Forum Monaco 2025" 
          class="w-full h-auto rounded-2xl shadow-2xl border border-white/20"
        />
        <p class="text-lg text-blue-200 mt-4 font-light italic">
          Christoph Schwager and Verena Sturm representing The Water Foundation at the Blue Economy & Finance Forum Monaco 2025
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Mission Statement -->
    <div class="mb-20">
      <div class="max-w-4xl">
        <div class="relative">
          <!-- Decorative Line -->
          <div class="absolute left-0 top-0 w-16 h-px bg-gradient-to-r from-cyan-400 to-blue-400"></div>
          
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-light text-white mb-6 tracking-wide">
            Our <span class="text-cyan-300 font-normal">Mission</span>
          </h2>
          
          <p class="text-xl text-blue-100 leading-relaxed font-light mb-8">
            The Water Foundation is a mission-driven entity acting as both a charitable organisation and strategic investor - anchoring a global capital stack to advance SDG 6 (Clean Water and Sanitation) and improve the lives of 1 billion people through resilient, equitable access to clean water.
          </p>
          
          <!-- Global Presence -->
          <div class="relative pl-8 border-l-2 border-cyan-400/30">
            <p class="text-lg text-blue-200 leading-relaxed font-light">
              Based in Dubai, Delhi, Vaduz, and Munich, we form an cross-border non-partisan initiative to enhance water resilience, affecting peace through socio-political stability, and creating net gains in shared prosperity through positive impacts on health, food, and land.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>



    <!-- Earth Image and Call to Action -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-12 items-center mb-20">
      <!-- Colorful Water Visualization -->
      <div class="group transform transition-all duration-500 hover:scale-105">
        <div class="relative w-full aspect-square overflow-hidden rounded-3xl border border-white/20 hover:border-white/40 transition-all duration-500">
          <!-- Organic Water Shapes -->
          <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-cyan-400 via-blue-500 to-teal-600">
            <!-- Large Four-Lobed Shape (Center) -->
            <div class="absolute top-1/2 left-1/2 transform -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2">
              <div class="w-32 h-32 animate-pulse">
                <svg viewBox="0 0 100 100" class="w-full h-full">
                  <path d="M50 20 Q60 15 70 20 Q75 30 70 40 Q60 45 50 40 Q40 45 30 40 Q25 30 30 20 Q40 15 50 20 Z M80 50 Q85 60 80 70 Q70 75 60 70 Q55 60 60 50 Q70 45 80 50 Z M50 80 Q40 85 30 80 Q25 70 30 60 Q40 55 50 60 Q60 55 70 60 Q75 70 70 80 Q60 85 50 80 Z M20 50 Q15 40 20 30 Q30 25 40 30 Q45 40 40 50 Q30 55 20 50 Z" 
                        fill="rgba(255,255,255,0.15)" 
                        stroke="rgba(255,255,255,0.3)" 
                        stroke-width="1.5"/>
                </svg>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <!-- Small Jagged Four-Lobed (Top Left) -->
            <div class="absolute top-1/4 left-1/4 w-16 h-16 animate-pulse" style="animation-delay: 0.5s;">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 100 100" class="w-full h-full">
                <path d="M50 15 Q65 10 75 20 Q80 35 70 45 Q55 50 45 40 Q35 50 20 45 Q10 35 15 20 Q25 10 50 15 Z M85 50 Q90 65 80 75 Q65 80 55 70 Q50 55 60 45 Q70 50 85 50 Z M50 85 Q35 90 25 80 Q20 65 30 55 Q45 50 55 60 Q65 50 80 60 Q90 65 85 80 Q75 90 50 85 Z M15 50 Q10 35 20 25 Q35 20 45 30 Q50 45 40 55 Q30 60 15 50 Z" 
                      fill="rgba(173,216,230,0.25)" 
                      stroke="rgba(173,216,230,0.4)" 
                      stroke-width="1"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            
            <!-- Small Rounded Five-Lobed (Bottom Left) -->
            <div class="absolute bottom-1/4 left-1/4 w-16 h-16 animate-pulse" style="animation-delay: 1s;">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 100 100" class="w-full h-full">
                <path d="M50 20 Q60 15 70 20 Q75 30 70 40 Q60 45 50 40 Q40 45 30 40 Q25 30 30 20 Q40 15 50 20 Z M80 50 Q85 60 80 70 Q70 75 60 70 Q55 60 60 50 Q70 45 80 50 Z M50 80 Q40 85 30 80 Q25 70 30 60 Q40 55 50 60 Q60 55 70 60 Q75 70 70 80 Q60 85 50 80 Z M20 50 Q15 40 20 30 Q30 25 40 30 Q45 40 40 50 Q30 55 20 50 Z M50 50 Q45 45 50 40 Q55 45 50 50 Z" 
                      fill="rgba(135,206,250,0.25)" 
                      stroke="rgba(135,206,250,0.4)" 
                      stroke-width="1"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            
            <!-- Large Jagged Four-Lobed (Right) -->
            <div class="absolute top-1/2 right-1/4 w-24 h-24 animate-pulse" style="animation-delay: 1.5s;">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 100 100" class="w-full h-full">
                <path d="M50 20 Q65 12 75 25 Q82 40 75 55 Q65 68 50 60 Q35 68 25 55 Q18 40 25 25 Q35 12 50 20 Z M85 50 Q92 65 80 75 Q65 82 50 75 Q35 82 20 75 Q8 65 15 50 Q8 35 20 25 Q35 18 50 25 Q65 18 80 25 Q92 35 85 50 Z M50 80 Q35 88 25 75 Q18 60 25 45 Q35 32 50 40 Q65 32 75 45 Q82 60 75 75 Q65 88 50 80 Z M15 50 Q8 35 20 25 Q35 18 50 25 Q65 18 80 25 Q92 35 85 50 Q92 65 80 75 Q65 82 50 75 Q35 82 20 75 Q8 65 15 50 Z" 
                      fill="rgba(64,224,208,0.25)" 
                      stroke="rgba(64,224,208,0.4)" 
                      stroke-width="1.5"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            
            <!-- Small Jagged Four-Lobed (Top Right) -->
            <div class="absolute top-1/4 right-1/4 w-16 h-16 animate-pulse" style="animation-delay: 0.5s;">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 100 100" class="w-full h-full">
                <path d="M50 15 Q65 10 75 20 Q80 35 70 45 Q55 50 45 40 Q35 50 20 45 Q10 35 15 20 Q25 10 50 15 Z M85 50 Q90 65 80 75 Q65 80 55 70 Q50 55 60 45 Q70 50 85 50 Z M50 85 Q35 90 25 80 Q20 65 30 55 Q45 50 55 60 Q65 50 80 60 Q90 65 85 80 Q75 90 50 85 Z M15 50 Q10 35 20 25 Q35 20 45 30 Q50 45 40 55 Q30 60 15 50 Z" 
                      fill="rgba(173,216,230,0.25)" 
                      stroke="rgba(173,216,230,0.4)" 
                      stroke-width="1"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            
            <!-- Small Rounded Five-Lobed (Bottom Right) -->
            <div class="absolute bottom-1/4 right-1/4 w-16 h-16 animate-pulse" style="animation-delay: 1s;">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 100 100" class="w-full h-full">
                <path d="M50 20 Q60 15 70 20 Q75 30 70 40 Q60 45 50 40 Q40 45 30 40 Q25 30 30 20 Q40 15 50 20 Z M80 50 Q85 60 80 70 Q70 75 60 70 Q55 60 60 50 Q70 45 80 50 Z M50 80 Q40 85 30 80 Q25 70 30 60 Q40 55 50 60 Q60 55 70 60 Q75 70 70 80 Q60 85 50 80 Z M20 50 Q15 40 20 30 Q30 25 40 30 Q45 40 40 50 Q30 55 20 50 Z M50 50 Q45 45 50 40 Q55 45 50 50 Z" 
                      fill="rgba(135,206,250,0.25)" 
                      stroke="rgba(135,206,250,0.4)" 
                      stroke-width="1"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            
            <!-- Subtle Background Pattern -->
            <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-10">
              <div class="absolute inset-0" style="background-image: radial-gradient(circle at 20% 20%, white 1px, transparent 1px), radial-gradient(circle at 80% 80%, white 1px, transparent 1px); background-size: 30px 30px;"></div>
            </div>
          </div>
          

        </div>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Call to action text -->
      <div class="lg:col-span-2 space-y-6">
        <div class="text-center py-8 font-avenir">
          <p class="text-5xl md:text-6xl lg:text-7xl font-black text-white mb-6 tracking-tighter leading-none drop-shadow-2xl">
            This is more than a crisis.
          </p>
          <p class="text-2xl md:text-3xl lg:text-4xl italic text-cyan-300 font-light tracking-wide leading-relaxed drop-shadow-lg">
            It's a call to invest in the future â€“ where innovation meets impact.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Investment Verticals Section -->
    <div class="mb-20">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-light text-white mb-8 tracking-wide">
          Our <span class="text-cyan-300 font-normal">Investment Verticals</span>
        </h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-blue-100 max-w-3xl mx-auto font-light">
          Strategic focus areas where we deploy capital and expertise to maximize impact and returns
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <!-- Water Venture Builder -->
        <div class="group transform transition-all duration-700 hover:scale-110 hover:-translate-y-4">
          <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-cyan-500/20 via-blue-500/20 to-teal-500/20 backdrop-blur-2xl border border-cyan-400/30 rounded-3xl p-10 h-full hover:bg-gradient-to-br hover:from-cyan-500/25 hover:via-blue-500/25 hover:to-teal-500/25 hover:border-cyan-400/50 transition-all duration-500 shadow-2xl hover:shadow-cyan-500/25">
            <div class="w-24 h-24 bg-gradient-to-br from-cyan-400/40 to-cyan-600/40 rounded-3xl flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-8 group-hover:scale-125 transition-transform duration-700">
              <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-gradient-to-br from-cyan-300 to-cyan-500 rounded-xl"></div>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-3xl font-light text-white text-center mb-6 tracking-wide">Water Venture Builder</h3>
            <p class="text-blue-100 text-center leading-relaxed mb-6 text-lg">
              We identify the best water IP/ideas, build teams around them, and provide the necessary capital and resources for success.
            </p>
            <div class="text-center">
              <span class="inline-block px-6 py-3 bg-gradient-to-r from-cyan-500/40 to-blue-500/40 text-cyan-100 text-lg font-light rounded-full border border-cyan-400/50">
                Core Strategy
              </span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Water VC Fund -->
        <div class="group transform transition-all duration-700 hover:scale-110 hover:-translate-y-4">
          <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-500/20 via-indigo-500/20 to-purple-500/20 backdrop-blur-2xl border border-blue-400/30 rounded-3xl p-10 h-full hover:bg-gradient-to-br hover:from-blue-500/25 hover:via-indigo-500/25 hover:to-purple-500/25 hover:border-blue-400/50 transition-all duration-500 shadow-2xl hover:shadow-blue-500/25">
            <div class="w-24 h-24 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-400/40 to-blue-600/40 rounded-3xl flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-8 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-700">
              <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-300 to-blue-500 rounded-xl"></div>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-3xl font-light text-white text-center mb-6 tracking-wide">Water VC Fund</h3>
            <p class="text-blue-100 text-center leading-relaxed mb-6 text-lg">
              We invest in the most promising existing teams and technologies, integrating them into the venture ecosystem to accelerate their growth.
            </p>
            <div class="text-center">
              <span class="inline-block px-6 py-3 bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-500/40 to-indigo-500/40 text-blue-100 text-lg font-light rounded-full border border-blue-400/50">
                Growth Focus
              </span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Water PE Fund -->
        <div class="group transform transition-all duration-700 hover:scale-110 hover:-translate-y-4">
          <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-teal-500/20 via-emerald-500/20 to-cyan-500/20 backdrop-blur-2xl border border-teal-400/30 rounded-3xl p-10 h-full hover:bg-gradient-to-br hover:from-teal-500/25 hover:via-emerald-500/25 hover:to-cyan-500/25 hover:border-teal-400/50 transition-all duration-500 shadow-2xl hover:shadow-teal-500/25">
            <div class="w-24 h-24 bg-gradient-to-br from-teal-400/40 to-teal-600/40 rounded-3xl flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-8 group-hover:scale-125 transition-transform duration-700">
              <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-gradient-to-br from-teal-300 to-teal-500 rounded-xl"></div>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-3xl font-light text-white text-center mb-6 tracking-wide">Water PE Fund</h3>
            <p class="text-blue-100 text-center leading-relaxed mb-6 text-lg">
              We acquire and enhance established players and hidden champions within the water cycle to build even greater impact and value.
            </p>
            <div class="text-center">
              <span class="inline-block px-6 py-3 bg-gradient-to-r from-teal-500/40 to-emerald-500/40 text-teal-100 text-lg font-light rounded-full border border-teal-400/50">
                Scale & Impact
              </span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <!-- Redefining Water Solutions Header -->
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-light text-white mb-8 tracking-wide">
        Redefining <span class="text-cyan-300 font-normal">Water Solutions</span>
      </h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-blue-200 max-w-3xl mx-auto font-light">
        A new paradigm for water security, resilience, and prosperity
      </p>
      <div class="w-32 h-px bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-blue-400 to-transparent mx-auto mt-8"></div>
    </div>
  

    <!-- Systems Thinkers Statement -->
    <div class="group transform transition-all duration-500 hover:scale-105 mb-16">
      <div class="bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-xl border border-white/20 rounded-3xl p-8 hover:bg-white/15 hover:border-white/30 transition-all duration-500">
        <p class="text-xl text-blue-100 italic font-light leading-relaxed text-center">
          What began as an improbable group of systems thinkers finding each other at COP29, grew into a targeted global initiative. We bring together exceptional people who are impatient with the way things are, embrace new ways of systems thinking across the water cycle and along the water tech stack - and have the courage to act.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Empowerment Section -->
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-20">
      <div class="group transform transition-all duration-500 hover:scale-105">
        <div class="bg-white/5 backdrop-blur-xl border border-white/10 rounded-2xl p-8 h-full hover:bg-white/10 hover:border-white/20 transition-all duration-500">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-light text-teal-300 mb-4">Strategic Capacity</h3>
          <p class="text-blue-100 leading-relaxed font-light">
            The Water Foundation empowers individuals, organisations, and states to develop strategic capacity, increase resilience, and shape circular water and resource infrastructures for the future - through knowledge, cooperation, and systemic innovation.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="group transform transition-all duration-500 hover:scale-105">
        <div class="bg-white/5 backdrop-blur-xl border border-white/10 rounded-2xl p-8 h-full hover:bg-white/10 hover:border-white/20 transition-all duration-500">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-light text-cyan-300 mb-4">Water Strategies</h3>
          <p class="text-blue-100 leading-relaxed font-light">
            We develop water strategies and solutions across the water cycle and for each and every water challenge. We enable the research, development and scaling of new or hidden technologies.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Quote Section -->
    <div class="relative my-20 py-12 px-8">
      <!-- Opening quote SVG -->
      <div class="absolute -top-4 left-0 w-24 h-24 text-cyan-400/20 -z-10">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" class="w-full h-full">
          <path d="M14.017 21v-7.391c0-5.704 3.731-9.57 8.983-10.609l.995 2.151c-2.432.917-3.995 3.638-3.995 5.849h4v10h-9.983zm-14.017 0v-7.391c0-5.704 3.748-9.57 9-10.609l.996 2.151c-2.433.917-3.996 3.638-3.996 5.849h3.983v10h-9.983z" />
        </svg>
      </div>
      
      <div class="bg-white/5 backdrop-blur-xl border border-white/20 rounded-3xl p-12">
        <p class="text-2xl italic text-center text-blue-100 relative z-10 font-light leading-relaxed">
          Where water security is achieved, <br> peace, socio-political stability and health follow.<br>
          <br>
          Where resilience is built by a water innovation ecosystem, <br> returns stabilize and become sustainable.<br>
          <br>
          And where water circularity drives productivity, <br> prosperity scales - both in impact and investment potential.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Closing quote SVG -->
      <div class="absolute -bottom-4 right-0 w-24 h-24 text-cyan-400/20 -z-10 transform rotate-180">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" class="w-full h-full">
          <path d="M14.017 21v-7.391c0-5.704 3.731-9.57 8.983-10.609l.995 2.151c-2.432.917-3.995 3.638-3.995 5.849h4v10h-9.983zm-14.017 0v-7.391c0-5.704 3.748-9.57 9-10.609l.996 2.151c-2.433.917-3.996 3.638-3.996 5.849h3.983v10h-9.983z" />
        </svg>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 mb-16">
      <!-- Water Crisis Today - Left Aligned -->
      <div class="text-left">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-foreground mb-4">The Water Crisis Today</h3>
        <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-red-500/10 to-orange-500/10 backdrop-blur-sm border-l-4 border-red-400/50 rounded-r-2xl p-6 transform transition-all duration-500 hover:scale-105 hover:translate-x-2">
          <p class="text-foreground/80 mb-2 leading-relaxed">
            While 90% of climate adaptation needs are water-based, less than 5% of climate finance is directed toward water solutions. 
            <span class="text-red-400 font-semibold">This critical gap is where we focus our efforts.</span>
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Our Vision for the Future - Right Aligned -->
      <div class="text-right">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-foreground mb-4">Our Vision for the Future</h3>
        <div class="bg-gradient-to-l from-cyan-500/10 to-blue-500/10 backdrop-blur-sm border-r-4 border-cyan-400/50 rounded-l-2xl p-6 transform transition-all duration-500 hover:scale-105 hover:-translate-x-2">
          <p class="text-foreground/80 mb-2 leading-relaxed">
            We envision a world where water security drives peace, stability, and prosperity for all. 
            <span class="text-cyan-400 font-semibold">Through innovation, investment, and collaboration, we're making this vision a reality.</span>
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="w-24 h-1 bg-primary mx-auto my-8"></div>

      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">
        <a href="/about" class="inline-flex items-center px-6 py-8 bg-primary text-white rounded-lg hover:bg-primary/90 transition-colors">
          Join Our Mission
          <svg class="ml-2 w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M14 5l7 7m0 0l-7 7m7-7H3"></path>
          </svg>
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>
